OL,3,CMan jailed for 14 years for 'violent,
OL,4,Cunprovoked' attack which killed dad
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 14 years for
OL,7,Fkilling a beloved father in a
OL,8,F"violent, unprovoked" attack.
OL,10,FSteven Chappell, 29, kicked and
OL,11,Fpunched pubgoer Daniel Bradley, 32,
OL,12,Fwhile he lay defenceless on the floor
OL,13,Fnear The Brogden pub, Porthcawl, in
OL,14,Fthe early hours of 9 September last
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FHe was found guilty of manslaughter at
OL,18,Ftrial, where he was acquitted of
OL,19,Fmurder.
