OL,3,CMan jailed for 14 years for 'violent,
OL,4,Cunprovoked' attack which killed dad
OL,6,FIn the early hours of September 9,
OL,7,F2023, Mr Bradley was walking down a
OL,8,Flane near the pub when he was
OL,9,Fassaulted twice by Chappell.
OL,11,FMr Bradley had been drinking in the
OL,12,Fpub that evening and was described as
OL,13,F"his normal self", joking and dancing
OL,14,Faround.
OL,16,FWhile in the lane by the pub, Chappell
OL,17,F- who was under the influence of
OL,18,Falcohol and drugs - had mistakenly
OL,19,Faccused Mr Bradley of owing his
OL,20,Fgirlfriend money.
