OL,3,CMan jailed for 14 years for 'violent,
OL,4,Cunprovoked' attack which killed dad
OL,6,FIn CCTV played to the court, the
OL,7,Fdefendant could be seen delivering
OL,8,Fkicks and punches to Mr Bradley as he
OL,9,Flay defenceless on the floor,
OL,10,Freturning to confront and attack
OL,11,F"quite timid and shy" Mr Bradley for a
OL,12,Fsecond time.
OL,14,FAfter Chappell had left the scene, Mr
OL,15,FBradley remained on the floor for 13
OL,16,Fminutes before he and girlfriend
OL,17,FCherelle McKay were able to get up and
OL,18,Fwalk away.
