OL,6,FThe court heard Chappell had "bragged"
OL,7,Fabout the assault after the incident,
OL,8,Fclaiming he did it because Mr Bradley
OL,9,F"had said something about (Chappell's)
OL,10,Fgirlfriend".
OL,12,FFollowing the assault, the court heard
OL,13,FMr Bradley was taken to hospital on
OL,14,FSeptember 11 after experiencing
OL,15,Fdifficulty breathing at home due to a
OL,16,Fbroken rib, and was discharged before
OL,17,Fan ambulance was called to his house
OL,18,Fon September 15.
