OL,6,FHe was suffering from severe sepsis,
OL,7,Fwhich caused multi-organ failure and
OL,8,Fcardiac arrest, causing irreversible
OL,9,Fbrain damage due to a lack of oxygen
OL,10,Fwhile his heart was not beating.
OL,12,FHe died in hospital on September 23,
OL,13,Faged 32, with his family at his
OL,14,Fbedside.
OL,16,FDuring Chappell's sentencing hearing
OL,17,Fon Monday, Mr Bradley's family
OL,18,Fdescribed their pain at the dad-of-
OL,19,Ftwo's loss as "unbearable".
