OL,6,FThey said: "Losing Dan has changed our
OL,7,Flives in ways we can't explain. Each
OL,8,Fday we get an overwhelming sense of
OL,9,Fsadness. Grief doesn't hit you on
OL,10,Fbirthdays or special occasions. It
OL,11,Faffects you every single second of
OL,12,Fevery single day. Everything feels
OL,13,Fincomplete. The only thing we have to
OL,14,Fremember Dan is our memories."
