OL,4,Cunprovoked' attack which killed dad
OL,6,FMr Bradley's father also described
OL,7,FChappell as a "coward" who has never
OL,8,Fsaid sorry for what happened. He
OL,9,Fadded: "Steven Chappell can be visited
OL,10,Fin prison by his children. They will
OL,11,Fbe able to speak to him over the phone
OL,12,Fand write letters to him. Dan's
OL,13,Fchildren will not have these
OL,14,Fprivileges."
OL,16,FAddressing the defendant at Newport
OL,17,FCrown Court, Judge Tracey Lloyd-Clarke
OL,18,Fdescribed the two assaults as a
OL,19,F"vicious attack", adding: "This was
OL,20,Fpersistent violence.
