OL,6,F"When you expressed emotions, it was
OL,7,Fto think of your children, not Mr
OL,8,FBradley's children, and how your
OL,9,Fchildren would feel if you had been
OL,10,Fthe victim... you are not truly
OL,11,Fremorseful.
OL,13,F"You are a man with a long history of
OL,14,Fviolence, you have minimised and
OL,15,Fjustified your violent behaviour and
OL,16,Fyou try to blame others."
