OL,3,CMan jailed for 14 years for 'violent,
OL,4,Cunprovoked' attack which killed dad
OL,6,FChappell, of Beechwood Avenue,
OL,7,FCwmdare, Aberdare, was handed an
OL,8,Fextended sentence of 16 years, made up
OL,9,Fof 14 years custody and an extended
OL,10,Flicence period of two years.
OL,12,FHe will serve two-thirds of the
OL,13,Fcustodial element in custody before he
OL,14,Fwill be considered for release. If
OL,15,Freleased at that point, he will serve
OL,16,Fthe remainder of the 14-year term on
OL,17,Flicence and then an extended licence
OL,18,Fperiod of two years will begin.
