OL,4,Cunprovoked' attack which killed dad
OL,6,FHe had appeared before the courts on
OL,7,Feight previous occasions for 17
OL,8,Foffences, including assault
OL,9,Foccasioning actual bodily harm,
OL,10,Fbattery, criminal damage, and
OL,11,Fpossession of drugs.
OL,13,FAddressing the victim's family, the
OL,14,Fjudge said: "To the family of Mr
OL,15,FBradley, I know that a sentence cannot
OL,16,Fease the terrible grief that you are
OL,17,Fsuffering, and it's not intended to
OL,18,Freflect the value of Daniel's life
OL,19,Fbecause that, of course, is beyond
OL,20,Fmeasure.
