OL,6,F"It's clear that he was very precious
OL,7,Fto you all, and he was dearly loved,
OL,8,Fnot only by his family, but by all who
OL,9,Fknew him.
OL,11,F"In addition to the terrible grief you
OL,12,Fare suffering, you've had to cope with
OL,13,Fthese proceedings. You have done so
OL,14,Fwith patience and dignity. Thank you.
OL,15,FThe court offers its sincere
OL,16,Fcondolences to you."
OL,18,FDetective Inspector Claire Lamerton,
OL,19,Fof South Wales Police, said: "Daniel
OL,20,Fsuffered a violent, unprovoked attack
OL,21,Ffrom Steven Chappell.
