OL,6,F"Daniel didn't represent any threat,
OL,7,Fand nothing happened that night that
OL,8,Fjustified what Steven Chappell did to
OL,9,FDaniel.
OL,11,F"Rather than walking away Steven
OL,12,FChappell's anger resulted in the
OL,13,Fassault on Daniel being excessive,
OL,14,Funnecessary, and completely reckless.
OL,16,F"This case shows what devastating
OL,17,Fconsequences attacks of this nature
OL,18,Fcan have. I would encourage others to
OL,19,Fthink about how easily a decision can
OL,20,Faffect the rest of your life and
OL,21,Fpotentially end someone else's.
